      • resolveRecipients

        List<String> resolveRecipients(se.inera.axel.shs.xml.label.ShsLabel label)
                               throws se.inera.axel.shs.exception.ShsException
        Resolves SHS To addresses (Organization Id's) based on information in the SHS label.

        May apply:

        • Direct addressing
        • Product addressing
        • Public agreement addressing
        • etc.
        Parameters:
        label -
        Returns:
        A list of organization id's of the message recipients, or the empty list.
        Throws:
        se.inera.axel.shs.exception.ShsException - if no recipient could be resolved due to an error.
